<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Whilst the $reset parameter is referenced in the method signature, it is never used in the URI assembly!</p>

<p>Suggest changing this:-</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $params = $data + $this-&gt;_values + $this-&gt;_defaults;
</code></pre>

<p>to this:-</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        if (!$reset) {
            $params = array_merge($this-&gt;_defaults, $this-&gt;_values);
        } else {
            $params = $this-&gt;_defaults;
        }
        
        $params = array_merge($params, $data);
</code></pre>

    </div>
